{"tid":999126,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"千萬不要來！","createTime":"2019-01-28T13:12:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T13:20:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6aa8e1fb27d0f4c6eda63abfb7c8201625f184c5","tid":999126,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T13:12:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/李碧華/daily/article/20190128/20600382\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190128%2F20600382&d=A8Zcnrt5rgz9w9jc%2F8WURJUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=366f48de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190128%2F20600382&h=e59c3fa5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/李碧華/daily/article/20190128/20600382</a><br />\n<br />\n2019年01月28日 <br />\n<br />\n千萬不要來！ - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190128/large/e8804a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190128%2Flarge%2Fe8804a.jpg&h=d4f0d88a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n最近一名東北的大陸遊客來港一趟，十分不滿，以「香港一日遊，再也不去了！」為題，在討論區發表文章，引起熱議。他筆下的香港有4宗罪：──<br />\n<br />\n（一）他經由港珠澳大橋過關，排隊時將煙從褲袋裏拿出來放手袋去，馬上有海關人員告知不許吸煙。<br />\n<br />\n（二）向巴士司機問話，他卻說一些不能明白的廣東話。<br />\n<br />\n（三）去海港城購物，無法使用支付寶，轉用信用卡又忘記了密碼&hellip;&hellip;收銀員「黑面」。<br />\n<br />\n（四）回程時想在免稅店購物不知價錢，店員着他「自己走到條裝櫃枱那邊去買」，像打發他走。<br />\n<br />\n這4宗「罪」？笑死！但大陸網民熱烈和應，還紛紛表示「反感，這輩子不去香港」、「再去香港旅遊我是狗，瑪德花錢去受氣？」、「老子有錢哪不能去？」、「沒我們來消費你們還沒工資發啊」&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n對對對！快廣傳。不用檢討不用照鏡也不必如恩主般自大，別再瞧得起香港和香港人了，大陸客的心聲，港人肯定、絕對、極度、超級贊同，千萬不要來，香港已淪落，不值一遊，一言既出駟馬難追，講得出做得到啊。<br />\n<br />\n還有，連討論、遠眺、過境也無謂，夢也別作──這是雙方的噩夢&hellip;&hellip;好了好了，一天光晒！  <br />\n<br />\n李碧華 <br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n全球最恐怖的笑話 (林夕)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n穿Chanel不知羞的女人 (鄧達智)"},{"pid":"88ac92d3e3613937e7fd88ca05557c3ca16d4ef4","tid":999126,"uid":103907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T13:20:14.000Z","msg":"口𥚃說不<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}